name: Dali | Gen7 Snappy Raised Brow
bio: Uh, hi! I'm Dali | Gen7 Snappy Raised Brow. I enjoy being a nevernude, tripping my owner, and breakdancing. When my owner isn't watching, I steal their brooches and use them for litter paper. I'm not sorry. We can be friends, but keep the ultra purrsonal stuff to yourself, please.
